---
title: Tex-Mex Style Turkey Skillet Rice with Sweet Bell Peppers and Cheddar Cheese
description: Cheese lovers, this one is for you! Succulent turkey is seasoned with our Mexican Seasoning in a hearty rice skillet with ooey gooey cheddar cheese on top.  A bonus delight comes from the deliciously crispy skillet bits at the bottom of the pan. May your cheese pulls be long and your meal time enjoyable!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poelee-de-riz-a-la-dinde-facon-tex-mex-18bb4b14.jpg
